If you live in a coastal community, Gov. Nikki Haley called for you to begin evacuating as early as Wednesday afternoon.
The evacuation is not mandatory, but it is strongly encouraged.
Edisto Island, Adams Run
Yonges Island, Meggett, Hollywood, Ravenel
Johns Island, Kiawah Island and Seabrook
James Island and Folly Beach
City of Charleston
North Charleston
East Cooper
Awendaw and McClellanville
Daniel Island
 
